
Create simple grid user identity:
idp
		+ [--storetype=<PKCS12|JKS|WIN>] 
		+ [--password=<keystore-password>]  
		+ [--alias] 
		+ [--pattern=<certificate/token pattern>] 
		+ [--validDuration=<duration-string>]  
		+ [<authentication source URL>] 
		+ <IDP service path> 
		+ <new IDP name>
		
Create Kerberos-based user identity:
idp
		+ [--kerbRealm=<Kerberos realm>] 
		+ [--kerbKdc=<Kerberos KDC>]  
		+ [--validDuration=<duration-string>]  
		+ <Kerberos IDP service path> 
		+ <Kerberos Id>		

Create GlobusAuth-based user identity:
idp
		+ [--validDuration=<duration-string>]  
		+ <Globus Auth IDP service path> 
		+ <Globus Auth Id>		


